---
description: Architecture and layout for Go backend
globs:
  - "backend/**/*.go"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Entrypoint in `/cmd/app/main.go`.
- Handlers in `/internal/handlers/`.
- Models in `/internal/models/`.
- Services in `/internal/services/`.
- Database code in `/internal/db/` using GORM.
- Keep packages cohesive; avoid cyclic dependencies.
- Prefer dependency injection for services.

